&ch00.xml;


An Introduction to &TeX;




, introduces
&TeX; and the tools that make up the &TeX; system.  It describes
various editing environments that simplify the job of editing &TeX;
documents.  It also discusses the mechanics of running &TeX; and
recovery from errors, and it provides an overview of &TeX; macro
packages and format files.



